Class GoodReadNotification

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.moniuliuma.android.decode.configuration.PropertyGroup
      • com.moniuliuma.android.decode.configuration.GoodReadNotification

  • public class GoodReadNotification
extends PropertyGroup
    GoodReadNotification is the class that configures which type of notification is activated on a successful read.
